{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The idea was if the Nazis had seen it, say, I'm so sorry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot about this, they were taking and presumably left me alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had this watch for a long while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I gave it to my son when he reached the age that I was at that time, close to 16, and was stolen from him, he lost it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was this, maybe-- this sort of gives you the idea of the kind of things you found, I mean, on the train.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a girl sitting with us, real younger than I, I think, maybe, say, 13, I don't know how old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was obviously an extremely confused young woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I asked a few questions, turned out she had been brought up by a loving Catholic couple-- Catholic-- and had been told, I think a couple of days before, she was adopted, she was really Jewish, and she better get out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No wonder she was a bit whoo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was wearing a little gold cross, OK?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some idiot told her, you know, spoke about how dangerous it was to have any gold and silver.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went into absolute panic, wanted to throw it out of the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, give it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she did, and I put it down the seat of the thing-- all right-- of the seat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well then suddenly, we hadn't seen a Nazi guard or heard of one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a bell sound on the-- on the track.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a moment later, a kid from the front coaches came into our apartment and said, we have crossed into Holland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are in Holland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think most of us didn't believe it, we were so, so amazed.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
